Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,OFF TO THE DEPARTMENT STORE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You want to join Dai's party?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With this last battle with the Dark Army,\Nwe saw that we have much to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We wish to join them and hone our skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you wait!\NI believe that should be my role!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy, you too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not let you have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I will join them on their journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's not fair, Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it not fair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-What give you the right?!\N-In these matters...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, all of you!\NYou three have a duty to protect Papunica!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm going with Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, can I talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A new weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This Steel Broadsword is on its last legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's off to Bengana Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bengana has a department store!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know?\NIt's a huge building filled with stores!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As big as an inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly. It's as big as a castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Father took me there once\Nwhen I was small.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was big and huge\Nand they had everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, would you like to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. I think it was like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-This is...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Mentor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no mistake.\NIt's the Dragon Crest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he really is a Dragon Knight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aban, your student\Nis far more than you knew!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So do you know what the mark\Nthat shows up on Dai's forehead is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My mistake. So you mentioned\Nyou want to journey with Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. Is that a no?\NI guess I'm still in training, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on. Consider these a parting gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorcerer Cape and Shining Staff\NI used when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Be there for Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to hit a major wall soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not as a Hero, but as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When that time comes,\Nyou have to support him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, he was awfully nice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,These seem pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing's kind of ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency! The balloon on the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:05:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's asleep from the Rariho spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry everybody!\NWe'll be right back, so don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She always does this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment my back is turned,\Nshe sneaks out of the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that just means\Npeace is returning to Papunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Dai is with her.\NThey should be fine for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly. After telling us we can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this, Leona?\NIsn't this stealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. How is my using\Npalace equipment stealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Shouldn't we have\Ninvited Popp, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp? Oh, right, that Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother? He doesn't seem too reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like he doesn't have much experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:07:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It probably wouldn't make\Na difference even if he came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why that little...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a lot more reliable than he looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? He's the type who runs away\Nthe moment the party is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And who asked you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was hoping to enjoy\Nan adventure alone with Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bengana is considered\Nthe safest country in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,With an advanced military and industry,\Nit's kept the Dark Army at bay
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,using its abundance of\Nweapons and resources
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,backed by the world's greatest economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Slow down a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal.\NI'm actually a little relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in Papunica,\NLeona has to be a leader for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So she seemed a little distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, she seems\Nmore lively and like herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're here\Nfor her stress relief or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! There's a castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.\NWhat castle has balloon like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona, you're going too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a department store?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge! Is it really full of stores?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing. It's a hundred times\Nbigger than my family weapon store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,4F CLOTHES, ARMOUR\N3F HOUSEHOLD ITEMS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't come here without\Nchecking out the basement!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,2F MAGIC ITEMS\N1F JEWELRY, COSMETICS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this room? It's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The room is falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. It's called an elevator\Nand it takes you to each floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's herbs and seeds\NI've never seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Two Slime Buns\Nand one Slime Tapioca please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing. That'll be ten gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are Slimes safe to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not real.\NIt's a snack shaped like a Slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? There's something inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations! You found a Small Medal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this thing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,3F HOUSEHOLD ITEMS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's super high-quality Horse Manure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so bright, I can't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Luxuries like these really make\Nthe department-store experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir. Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a nice buckle there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean. Isn't it ugly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a wonderful buckle.\NI'll pay you 500 gold for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,500 gold?! That much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. It's definitely cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.56,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:11.56,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}HELL'S CLAW{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirs! See my latest product! Both attack\Nand defense in this all-purpose helm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Blockhead Basher!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy one now and I'll throw in\Nanother one for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't these sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. This is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! 3,800 gold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I shouldn't have touched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, feel free to buy anything\Nless than 5,000 gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Metals and cloth\Nfrom Papunica sell for a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If I sell these dresses,\Nit should get us 20 to 30,000 gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a real princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:18.30,On Top,,0,0,0,,DRESSING ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.57,0:12:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of Sage dresses like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wear something more serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on.\NThis actually has pretty high defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good. I got a new weapon\Nand cape already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You pick something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! I'll get used to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's find Dai a new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I don't feel much stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A Dragonsbane!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The famous weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It can pierce a Dragon's hide,\Nwhich is said to be harder than steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a top quality weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's expensive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no price.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends, this is our only piece,\Nso it will be put on auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,An auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, these things\Ngo for over 15,000 Gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't buy it\Nwith Mommy's allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, Popp, let's buy that Dragonsbane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have 16,000 gold right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Using weapons more powerful than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your money like one of\Nthose fools pretending to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:15:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive us.\NMy grandmother has a foul mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely call them as I see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They looked like Seers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But the young one\Nwas kind of cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This country's finished.\NAll that's advanced is its appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Meruru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother, something's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Many monsters with terrifying power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I haven't sensed anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru, it seems you've developed\Nour bloodline's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming! They're close!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A Hydra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our cannon's aren't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how tough is its hide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,17,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,17,500!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,18,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Princess. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already 2,000 gold over our limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If no one else will bid, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine! I've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,19--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sold! Today's feature item,\Nthe Dragonsbane,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,has been sold to the merchant,\NMr. Gopple, for 18,000 gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly! What are you doing, Gomechan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Leona.\NI can fight with a normal weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't stand letting those goons\Nhave such a good weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be far better in our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,An army of Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see one Hydra, and Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Five Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the Dragon Legion\Nof the Dark Army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You bought the Dragonsbane, right?!\NUse it to drive them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!\NI bought this to make money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, with that many Dragons,\Nwe might be in over our heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fight! We should fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Dragons might have\Ncome here seeking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we should buy time\Nso that everyone can evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'll even protect people like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, you've changed\Nmy opinion about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess true leaders\Nprove themselves under fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:19:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My opinion of you\Nstill hasn't changed though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, I'll take care of the Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You take the big guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, you evacuate the people in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on people!\NWe need to get out of here! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess five Dragons is a little much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! In that case!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you how fast I've learned\Nto flee from all my battles!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Meruru! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to help those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What can simple Seers like us do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Seers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew when to run because we could\Nforesee when the Dark Army was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We've survived\Nby moving from town to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of fleeing towns, knowing\Nmany people will be hurt or killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Meruru, wait! Meruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Help my mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to move this rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Wave Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:25.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:32.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:36.02,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:43.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:46.53,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:52.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:57.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:23:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:23:01.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:08.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:13.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:19.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An army of Dragons\Nattacks the Bengana castle town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Using the power of his mark, Dai faces\Na giant Dragon with a hide of steel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Seers Nabara and Meruru watch\Nthe battle and are shocked by Dai's mark.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What truth will Nabara reveal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:23:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Dragon Knight"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:24:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
